The list archives will continue to be available to browse.<br><br>We can reactivate this list if we can find a new list owner. To volunteer please contact us at helpline@jiscmail.ac.uk - we can provide training and support. We have contacted the people who run the list (list owners) to decide on the future of the list, but have not received a response.<br><br>We plan to close and RETAIN the list **w/c 7th July 2014** [...]   </description>   <dc:date>2014-06-11T17:44:07+01:00</dc:date>   <dc:creator>JiscMail Helpline</dc:creator>   <dc:identifier>https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=CREATIVE-MANAGEMENT;f9e17e4.1406</dc:identifier> </item>   </rdf:RDF>
